trait-bogan-accent-name = Bogan Accent
trait-bogan-accent-desc = Oi! You speaking like a Yowie!

# Physical
trait-prybar-prosthetics-name = Prybar Prosthetics
trait-prybar-prosthetics-desc = [italic]Your arms are replaced with steel-and-hydraulic bionic prybar arms.[/italic]

    • The prybar arms can force open things bare hands can't.

trait-vigor-name = Vigor
trait-vigor-desc = [italic]Whether by pure determination, fitness, or bionic augmentations, your endurance is enhanced.[/italic]

    • Stamina increased by 10 points.
    • Stamina regen increased by 0.6 per second.
    • Regen starts 2.25 seconds after taking stamina damage, instead of 3.

trait-lethargy-name = Lethargy
trait-lethargy-desc = [italic]You become tired faster than others, making you more vulnerable to exhaustion and fatigue.[/italic]

    • Stamina decreased by 15 points.
    • Stamina regen decreased by 0.6 per second.
    • Regen starts 3.75 seconds after taking stamina damage, instead of 3.

trait-glass-jaw-name = Glass Jaw
trait-glass-jaw-desc = [italic]Your body is more fragile than others, more susceptible to critical injuries.[/italic]

    • Critical threshold decreased by 10 points.

trait-tenacity-name = Tenacity
trait-tenacity-desc = [italic]Through raw grit, willpower, or subtle bionic augmentations, you are hardier than others.[/italic]

    • Critical threshold increased by 5 points.

trait-will-to-live-name = Will to Live
trait-will-to-live-desc = [italic]You have an unusually strong "will to live", and resist death more than others.[/italic]

    • Death threshold increased by 10 points.

trait-will-to-die-name = Will to Die
trait-will-to-die-desc = [italic]You have an unusually weak "will to live", and succumb to injuries sooner than others.[/italic]

    • Death threshold decreased by 15 points.

trait-thieving-name = Thieving
trait-thieving-desc = [italic]You are deft with your hands, and talented at relieving people of their belongings.[/italic]

    • Strip and pickpocket 50% faster.
    • Can identify items hidden in pockets.

trait-bionic-legs-name = Bionic Legs
trait-bionic-legs-desc = [italic]One or more of your legs have been replaced with an expensive, state-of-the-art bionic, whether realistic synthflesh or an obvious metal limb.[/italic]

    • Move faster on foot.

trait-osteogenesis-imperfecta-name = Osteogenesis Imperfecta
trait-osteogenesis-imperfecta-desc = [italic]Also known as "brittle bone disease": your bones break easily, sometimes simply from moving.[/italic]

    • Critical threshold decreased by 50 points.

trait-hemophilia-name = Hemophilia
trait-hemophilia-desc = [italic]Your body's ability to form blood clots is impaired.[/italic]

    • Bleed for roughly twice as long.
    • Take 10% more Blunt damage.

trait-voracious-name = Voracious
trait-voracious-desc = [italic]Nothing gets between you and your food.[/italic]

    • Eat and drink twice as fast.

trait-bionic-spinarette-name = Bionic Spinarette
trait-bionic-spinarette-desc = [italic]A vatgrown organ implanted below the wrist that converts bodily lipids into all-natural silk, spun from an opening in the palm.[/italic]

    • Spin silk from an action, at the cost of hunger.

trait-feeble-name = Feeble
trait-feeble-desc = [italic]Your body responds poorly to injuries, so damage slows your movement more severely.[/italic]

    • For most species: 30% slower at 45 damage, 54% slower at 65 damage.

trait-trap-avoider-name = Trap Avoider
trait-trap-avoider-desc = [italic]You possess a preternatural sense of traps, and unconsciously avoid them.[/italic]

    • Never trigger floor traps (land mines, tripwires, mouse traps, etc.).

trait-self-aware-name = Self-Aware
trait-self-aware-desc = [italic]You possess a keen intuition of your body and senses.[/italic]

    • Examine your own wounds and burns precisely, like a health analyzer.
    • Gauge your own toxin and airloss damage.

trait-liquor-lifeline-name = Liquor Lifeline
trait-liquor-lifeline-desc = [italic]Forget the doctor — just hit the bar for your "ethanol prescription"![/italic]

    • While drunk, slowly heal Brute, Heat, Shock, and Cold damage, scaling with how drunk you are.
    • Your liver is replaced with a dwarven one, granting Alcohol Tolerance.

trait-redshirt-name = Redshirt
trait-redshirt-desc = [italic]"They said this air would be breathable. Get in, get out again, and no one gets hurt. Something is pulling me up the hill. I look down in my red shirt. I look down in my red shirt."[/italic]

    • Death threshold reduced by 100 points.

trait-striking-calluses-name = Striking Calluses
trait-striking-calluses-desc = [italic]An iconic enhancement from the world of cyber-enhanced martial arts: bony dermal deposits (or hard plastic shells for prosthetics) reinforce your knuckles.[/italic]

    • Unarmed strikes deal 2 more damage.
    • No benefit to armed melee.

trait-steadfast-name = Steadfast
trait-steadfast-desc = [italic]When others would buckle under their injuries, you still march forward unrelentingly.[/italic]

    • For most species, reduces movement slow from damage: 17% at 70 damage, 30% at 90 damage.

trait-dermal-armor-name = Dermal Armor
trait-dermal-armor-desc = [italic]Your skin has been replaced with a flexible but sturdy hard-polymer shell wrapped in synthetic flesh.[/italic]

    • 3.5 flat reduction to Blunt, Slash, and Piercing damage.
    • Take 25% more Shock damage.

trait-ironman-name = Ironman
trait-ironman-desc = [italic]You live strictly on hard cash.[/italic]

    • Cannot withdraw from your bank account.
    • Start the shift with a ship voucher.

trait-temperature-tolerance-name = Temperature Tolerance
trait-temperature-tolerance-desc = [italic]You have a notable tolerance for the cold.[/italic]

    • Endure conditions just below freezing for extended periods, like a walk-in fridge.

trait-alcohol-tolerance-name = Alcohol Tolerance
trait-alcohol-tolerance-desc = [italic]Your body shrugs off the visual effects of booze.[/italic]

    • Drinks blur your vision far less.
    • Does not affect alcohol poisoning or how drunk you become.

trait-platelet-factories-name = Platelet Factories
trait-platelet-factories-desc = [italic]Bio-tailored organs that keep you alive in the face of advanced trauma, up until — but not including — death.[/italic]

    • Slowly heal Brute and Burn damage on your own.

trait-nanite-repair-drones-name = Nanite Repair Drones
trait-nanite-repair-drones-desc = [italic]Repair drones course through your chassis, responding to physical trauma.[/italic]

    • Slowly self-repair Brute and Burn damage (the silicon equivalent of Platelet Factories).

trait-hardened-lymphocytes-name = Hardened Lymphocytes
trait-hardened-lymphocytes-desc = [italic]Your marrow has been treated with melanocyte-hardened stem cells that abate radiation.[/italic]

    • 1 flat reduction to Radiation damage; suitable for light salvage and mining.
